{"tid":423830,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"對你黎講，錢買唔買到快樂？","createTime":"2017-10-04T08:34:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T12:18:36.000Z","uid":16652,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b4ff012a2ca1f3fdbf94a8a5d9578e1042bb2e7d","tid":423830,"uid":16652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:34:25.000Z","msg":"剛剛我去買吃的 繞了好幾圈 吃膩了 不知吃什麼 就隨便吃了炒飯並不好吃<br />\n <br />\n而且下雨天 沒車只能穿雨衣騎車 吃飯時 袋子上都水；回到家 吃飯 看到長毛壁癌<br />\n <br />\n配著掉粉的油漆 明明就吸了很多 騙自己沒看到還裝作沒事 還開著電風扇、冷氣<br />\n <br />\n吹著整個整間都是 裝著不知道；為了維持生活 要看一些機巴人臉色 很不爽賺錢<br />\n <br />\n竟然有人說「錢買不到快樂」 到底是誰講的? 我不敢說 有錢過得多好 開好車 住好房<br />\n <br />\n至少不用受氣"},{"pid":"47a9547cf5cea6ff8861e2da29ae61d63acfcda7","tid":423830,"uid":3947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:35:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3638b315442d09b5fe0f08c0bf168f82a9d9c89","tid":423830,"uid":32583,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:35:37.000Z","msg":"有資格講錢買不到快樂的人一定要係有錢人<br />\n而不是窮人講的"},{"pid":"8b7b2536dfb91de264e746f82493fc9f81b52ebf","tid":423830,"uid":16652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:38:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有資格講錢買不到快樂的人一定要係有錢人<br />\n而不是窮人講的</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你講得岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5c92a2c0f7ac954779e0114f1a74a4e6bf74ab","tid":423830,"uid":79266,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:49:30.000Z","msg":"我揾錢就係想自己開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307c5dc025062cfd87f3075c5d8db835522b37b7","tid":423830,"uid":143241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:52:41.000Z","msg":"錢的確係買唔到快樂,但唔通你窮就好快樂？"},{"pid":"7e2557e0415bf2ee3328d3ebf4c8e3d7f7496e06","tid":423830,"uid":149664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:55:29.000Z","msg":"扮乜撚野台仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07fa3865c7a6520141f0e293f5ed2307be1a2ffe","tid":423830,"uid":143391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:57:59.000Z","msg":"可以 但只係短暫既快樂"},{"pid":"ef40f15b7ded16041e221652c6657d2db1ff6979","tid":423830,"uid":145923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:59:42.000Z","msg":"有錢一樣要受氣"},{"pid":"d4334dc5eefe24794ad120158c97490f7d8691ed","tid":423830,"uid":72173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T09:39:01.000Z","msg":"有錢到不愁衣食我就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知係咪窮到無求無慾<br />\n<br />\n飛機無搭過 無出過國<br />\n朋友成日講去邊到邊到旅行<br />\n我都只可以苦笑聽下<br />\n我唔恨去旅行，<br />\n但有時真係好想離開香港睇下依個世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8f3baafb1e10c9b4e32260ba5911abb7fd7113c","tid":423830,"uid":9436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T09:45:58.000Z","msg":"買到 話買唔到係因為你唔夠多錢"},{"pid":"8f88932245d44758ef6f1b8d821bcc9b7a306d9e","tid":423830,"uid":78522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T09:47:36.000Z","msg":"買到 不過唔係你快樂<br />\n係賺你錢個d人快樂"},{"pid":"cb621abe9dae2bb3f34804e309516dabbd9221ec","tid":423830,"uid":39383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T12:18:36.000Z","msg":"我買到，有錢就有快樂"}]}